#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:1
msgid "使用交易策略"
msgstr "Using Trading Strategies"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:3
msgid ""
"在 qteasy 中，交易策略（Strategy）负责在每一个运行周期内根据历史数据生成交易信号；Operator "
"是策略的容器与调度器，负责按既定频率与时间点运行策略并汇总信号；多个策略可归为 Group，同一 Group 内可通过 blender "
"表达式混合信号。"
msgstr ""
"In qteasy, a trading strategy (``Strategy``) generates trading signals from historical data at each run "
"step; ``Operator`` is the container and scheduler that runs strategies at configured frequencies and "
"times and aggregates signals; multiple strategies form a ``Group``, and signals within the same Group can "
"be blended via a ``blender`` expression."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:5
msgid "总体介绍"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:7
msgid "**Strategy**：根据 DataType 获取的数据和可调参数，在 ``realize()`` 中计算并返回信号（如目标仓位、选股列表等）。"
msgstr ""
"**Strategy**: Uses data from ``DataType`` and tunable parameters to compute and return signals in "
"``realize()`` (e.g., target positions or stock-selection lists)."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:8
msgid ""
"**Operator**：持有若干 Strategy，配置 "
"``signal_type``（PT/PS/VS）、``run_freq``、``run_timing``，在回测或实盘时按时间步调用策略并产出统一格式的信号。"
msgstr ""
"**Operator**: Holds one or more ``Strategy`` instances, configures ``signal_type`` (PT/PS/VS), "
"``run_freq``, and ``run_timing``, and invokes strategies step by step in backtest or live trading to "
"produce signals in a unified format."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:9
msgid ""
"**Group**：相同 ``run_freq`` 与 ``run_timing`` 的策略会被归入同一 Group；每个 Group 可配置 "
"blender 将多策略信号合并。"
msgstr ""
"**Group**: Strategies sharing the same ``run_freq`` and ``run_timing`` belong to one Group; each Group "
"can configure a ``blender`` to merge multiple strategy signals."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:11
msgid "主要内容概览"
msgstr "Main Topics"

