msgstr "**Creating and configuring Operator**: See *2. Operator: Creation and Basic Configuration*."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:14
msgid "**Group 与 blender**：见《3. Group 与策略信号混合》。"
msgstr "**Group and blender**: See *3. Group and Strategy Signal Blending*."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:15
msgid "**内置策略的查找与使用**：见《4. 内置策略的查找与使用》。"
msgstr "**Finding and using built-in strategies**: See *4. Finding and Using Built-in Strategies*."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:16
msgid "**三种策略基类**：RuleIterator、FactorSorter、GeneralStg，见《5. 三种策略基类》。"
msgstr ""
